<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SQL JOIN </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>子句用于把来自两个或多个表的行结合起来。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>连接表时需要在每个表中选择一个字段，并对这些字段的值进行比较，值相同的两条记录将合并为一条。本质就是将不同表的记录合并起来，形成一张新的临时表，查询结束后删除。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#333333'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MySQL</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的缓存的大小能够由</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>join_buffer_size</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>参数进行设置。同一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SQL</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>多关联（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>join</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）一个表，就会多分配一个关联缓存，若是在一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SQL</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中关联的表越多，所占用的内存也就越大。如果量的使用了多表关联的操作，同时</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>join_buffer_size</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>设置的也不合理的状况下，就容易形成服务器内存溢出的状况，就会影响到服务器数据库性能的稳定性</span></li>
</ul>
